{
  "stem": "23742.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was definitely not for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had developed some kind of managerial capacity.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I took a job as a salesman at a furniture store.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could talk to people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I changed a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I drifted back into the clothing industry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I became a salesman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I traveled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went to night school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I studied.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When I left school at 14, I was very much an under-average scholar.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But life teaches you a great deal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I progressed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can remember highlights.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, in five and a half years, you can-- an awful lot has happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some very-- there were some times when, yes, life is extremely difficult.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were times when my life was in danger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Perhaps not so dangerous as other men who fought in the services.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yes, I belonged to the Association of Jewish Ex-servicemen and Women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we have meetings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we have gatherings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we talk about the past.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We perpetuate the memories of our colleagues who never came back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And even until today, we still are active as Jewish ex-servicemen and women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We have a memorial room in East London-- both of the 1418 wars and the '39 wars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We have some very heroic men of our religion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We have members of the Victoria Cross, who earned very high gallantry awards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we still have annual remembrance parades in Whitehall, which as the years go by, of course, unfortunately become less and less, which we are very concerned about.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we do make every attempt to make sure that what the Jewish people did during the war was of significant contribution.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
